## 2. Button Patterns

| Type | Context | Classes |
|------|---------|---------|
| **Primary** | Hero CTA, main actions | `bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/90 via-secondary/90 to-accent/90 text-white rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:scale-105` |
| **Secondary** | Cancel, alternative | `bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600` |
| **Danger** | Delete, destructive | `bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white rounded-xl` |
| **Icon Only** | Table actions | `p-1.5 rounded-lg text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/30` |
| **Filter Tab Active** | Filter buttons | `bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:bg-primary/20 dark:text-primary-light rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5` |
| **Filter Tab Inactive** | Filter buttons | `text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5` |

### Button PROHIBITED Patterns:

```svelte
<!-- WRONG: White/transparent in hero -->
<button class="bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30">

<!-- WRONG: No hover effects -->
<button class="bg-primary">

<!-- WRONG: Non-rounded -->
<button class="rounded">  <!-- Should be rounded-xl or rounded-lg -->
```

