## 7. Color System

**MANDATORY: Use primary/secondary/accent only. NO custom colors (blue, amber, purple, etc.)**

| Usage | Light Mode | Dark Mode |
|-------|------------|-----------|
| Primary button | `from-primary/90 via-secondary/90 to-accent/90` | Same |
| Primary subtle | `bg-primary/10 text-primary` | `bg-primary/20 text-primary-light` |
| Card background | `bg-white/60` | `bg-gray-800/60` |
| Text primary | `text-gray-900` | `text-gray-100` |
| Text secondary | `text-gray-600` | `text-gray-300` |
| Text muted | `text-gray-500` | `text-gray-400` |
| Border | `border-white/20` | `border-gray-700/30` |

